These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: mexican, british, australian, chinese
1. Nationality:british is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:chinese is between Nationality:mexican and Nationality:british##2
3. Nationality:chinese is on the right of Nationality:mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | mexican | chinese | british | australian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: blueberry, cranberry, corn, lettuce
1. Food:blueberry is on the left of Food:lettuce##1
2. Food:cranberry is in an odd position##4
3. Food:cranberry is on the left or right of Food:blueberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | cranberry | blueberry | lettuce | corn |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: western, fantasy, epic, musical
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:western##3
2. Movie-Genre:western is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:epic is between Movie-Genre:musical and Movie-Genre:fantasy##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical | epic | fantasy |

 #################################
 
