.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: lettuce, grapes, cabbage, mango
1. Food:grapes == Food:grapes##1
2. Food:mango is on the left or right of Food:cabbage##3
3. Food:cabbage is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:lettuce is in an even position##4
5. Food:mango is on the left of Food:grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | cabbage | mango | grapes | lettuce |

